'''Dish Network'''是[[美國|美國]][[科羅拉多州|科羅拉多州]][[恩格爾伍德_(科羅拉多州)|恩格爾伍德]]的一家[[衛星廣播|衛星廣播]]服務提供商，為美國用戶提供[[衛星電視|衛星電視]]、[[衛星網絡|衛星網絡]]、廣播、[[移动通信|移动通信]]等服務。截至2019年，該公司服務訂閱者有將近一千一百三十萬人。它本是1996年3月[[EchoStar|EchoStar]]建立的一个品牌，2008年1月自EchoStar中分拆出來。

== 历史 ==
2011年4月，Dish Network以2.33億美元的價格收購了[[百視達|百視達]]和所剩下1,700家商店，並由前者負擔其8700萬美元的債務。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://articles.latimes.com/2011/apr/07/business/la-fi-ct-dish-blockbuster-20110407 |title=Dish Network wins bidding for assets of bankrupt Blockbuster |work=Los Angeles Times |accessdate=2011-05-02 |first=Ben |last=Fritz |date=2011-04-07 |archive-date=2011-04-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110421034918/http://articles.latimes.com/2011/apr/07/business/la-fi-ct-dish-blockbuster-20110407 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2015年，Dish Network在[[联邦通信委员会|FCC]]所举行的{{le|先进无线服务|Advanced Wireless Services|AWS-3}}频谱{{le|AWS-3拍卖|AWS-3 auction|拍卖}}中购得大量频谱，意图进军移动通信业。

2019年宣布收购[[Sprint|Sprint]]旗下预付费品牌{{le|Boost Mobile}}和800 MHz频谱。2020年7月1日完成收购Boost Mobile<ref name=":0">{{cite web|title=Dish buys prepaid carrier Boost Mobile for $1.4 billion|url=https://www.engadget.com/dish-acquires-boost-mobile-wireless-carrier-171217646.html|access-date=2020-07-01|website=Engadget|language=en|archive-date=2020-07-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200704090815/https://www.engadget.com/dish-acquires-boost-mobile-wireless-carrier-171217646.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":1">{{cite web|title=T‑Mobile Closes Deal with DISH to Divest Sprint Prepaid Business|url=https://www.t-mobile.com/news/un-carrier/t-mobile-closes-deal-with-dish-to-divest-sprint-prepaid-business|access-date=2020-07-01|website=T-Mobile Newsroom|archive-date=2020-07-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200703131444/https://www.t-mobile.com/news/un-carrier/t-mobile-closes-deal-with-dish-to-divest-sprint-prepaid-business|dead-url=no}}</ref>，并设立子公司Dish Wireless负责运营移动通信业务。800 MHz频谱将在2023年前完成收购。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://about.dish.com/2019-07-26-DISH-to-Become-National-Facilities-based-Wireless-Carrier |title=DISH to Become National Facilities-based Wireless Carrier |date=2019-07-26 |website=DISH Newsroom |access-date=2021-05-01 |archive-date=2021-04-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210424150633/https://about.dish.com/2019-07-26-DISH-to-Become-National-Facilities-based-Wireless-Carrier |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2020年8月1日，收购{{le|Ting|Ting Inc.|Ting Mobile}}。<ref>{{Cite press release|last=Inc|first=Tucows|date=2020-08-03|title=DISH selects Tucows as technology partner, acquires Ting Mobile assets|url=http://www.globenewswire.com/news-release/2020/08/03/2071636/0/en/DISH-selects-Tucows-as-technology-partner-acquires-Ting-Mobile-assets.html|access-date=2020-08-03|website=GlobeNewswire News Room|archive-date=2021-04-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210430205357/http://www.globenewswire.com/news-release/2020/08/03/2071636/0/en/DISH-selects-Tucows-as-technology-partner-acquires-Ting-Mobile-assets.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2021年3月8日，宣布计划收购{{le|Republic Wireless}}。<ref>{{Cite press release|date=2021-03-08|title=DISH to acquire Republic Wireless|url=https://about.dish.com/2021-03-08-DISH-to-acquire-Republic-Wireless|access-date=2021-03-10|archive-date=2021-05-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210501162129/https://about.dish.com/2021-03-08-DISH-to-acquire-Republic-Wireless|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite press release|last=Chuang|first=Chris|date=2021-03-10|title=A Letter from Our CEO: Republic Wireless Joins DISH!|url=https://forums.republicwireless.com/t/a-letter-from-our-ceo-republic-wireless-joins-dish|access-date=2021-03-10}}</ref>

